so I gave Bagheera a box....
What did Bagheera do with the Box?
You guys ever watch Happy Death Day?
No, but I read the plot on wikipedia because it didn't seem like my kind of film.
Groundhog Day, but day resets when she dies <3
Best part is that as she realizes what's going on, she embraces it
Quite a few deaths where she went, "You have got to be kidding me."  Because the killer comes out of nowhere and always seems to know where she is
Not sure if they'll do a third film...  2nd one had a pretty good explanation for the time loop
I prefer Edge of Tomorrow loopwise
Quill, you ever see The Butterfly Effect?
So yeah, Happy Death Day is basically Edge of Tomorrow + The Butterfly Effect in most regards
Death restarts the protagonist to the start of the day
I remember the plot well enough from wikipedia
In The Butterfly Effect, the change was his memories in his brain
With Happy Death Day, the injuries that cause her death leave scar tissues in the affected organs
So the movie is a race against the clock.  Yes, she has "infinite" deaths, but eventually the damage will be too much and she'll die for good
Adds a nice twist to the loop.
Is a nice juxtaposition to her flippant attitude of earlier deaths where they were legit "OH COME ON!" moments
Camping in a bush with black clothing, camo face paint, and some twigs to spy on someone you suspect?
